&lt;li&gt;Produce application videos that show Apera&#39;s 4D Vision technology solving real automation challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a library of application-specific video content across use cases such as bin picking, machine tending, sorting, packaging, assembly, and other robotic vision applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create short-form clips for LinkedIn, YouTube, SDR outreach, paid media, website pages, retargeting, webinar follow-up, and event follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edit raw footage from engineering, demos, trade shows, customers, partners, and integrators into polished, usable marketing assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add captions, motion graphics, annotations, diagrams, and simple explainers that make technical content easier to understand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand and Campaign Content&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
